formatTokenURI(string).notice: Helper Function - take an Image URI and create the full token URI JSON object Steps Taken: - Build a JSON object with all the fields we want in the metadata - has to return a base64 encoded object though

svgToImageURI(string).notice: Helper Function - take an SVG and create a distinct URI Steps Taken: - take the svg and base 64 encode it - add it to the string "data:image/svg+xml;base64,<Base64EncodingOfSVG>"
